# OnTrack

Meal planner & budgeter — **FastAPI** backend (`backend/`) + **Next.js** frontend (`frontend-next/`).

## Non-negotiable

- **API contract:** `docs/backend-migration/API_CONTRACT.md`, `frontend-next/lib/api/*.ts`, OpenAPI snapshot in CI
- **Auth response:** `{ "token": "..." }` — not `{ access_token, refresh_token }` unless contract is updated
- **Do not push to `main`** — use PR + green CI (`.github/DEPLOY.md`)
- **Never commit** `.env` or secrets
- **Production frontend:** `frontend-next/` only — not `frontend/` (CRA reference)

## Stack

| Layer | Runtime |
|-------|---------|
| API | FastAPI `backend/app/` |
| Frontend | Next.js App Router `frontend-next/` |
| DB | PostgreSQL 15, Alembic in `backend/alembic/` |
| Deploy | Railway + GitHub Actions |

## Legacy (reference only)

- `frontend/` — CRA snapshot for parity comparison; see `frontend/README.md`
- `docs/backend-migration/` — cutover history; FastAPI is production
